  - {fileID: 1109318122}
  - {fileID: 1294997643}
  objectiveLabels:
  - Independent auditor se majority, oath, assets and conflict register verify karein
  - Twelve-member cabinet ka public disclosure and recusal register publish karein
  - Costed priorities, debt limit and contingency reserve ke saath open budget lock
    karein
  - Medicine, maternal referral, ambulance and hospital grievance command activate
    karein
  - Teacher support, foundational learning and dropout outreach baseline karein
  - Shanti-led safety and access forum se accountable action owners fix karein
  - Open district dashboard ya centralized headline drive ka governance decision
    lein
  - Eighteen fictional districts ka receipt-to-appeal grievance dashboard run karein
  - Samrat ke saath heat, flood, crowd and missing-child response drill pass karein
  - Tender, conflict, price, delivery and appeal records ka red-flag audit karein
  - Residents, opposition and press ke saath equal-time 100-day jan sunwai karein
  - Independent panel par delivery, integrity, fiscal and full-term result dekhein
  milestoneSteps: 03000000070000000a000000
  milestoneTitles:
  - CABINET AND BUDGET OPEN
  - DELIVERY MODEL ACTIVE
  - STATE SYSTEMS AUDITED
  milestoneMessages:
  - Mandate, cabinet and budget records public hain. Health, education and safety
    delivery next hai.
  - Health, learning, safety and governance model active hain. District execution
    and audits next hain.
  - Grievance, disaster and procurement systems audited. Open jan sunwai final review
    unlock karegi.
